            #1. Classic Synthetic Control
        &lt;/h2&gt;
        &lt;div class="code-block"&gt;
* Load and prepare data cnuse synth_smoking.dta, clear tsset state year
label variable cigsale “per-capita cigarette sales (in packs)” label variable year “Year”
* Run synthetic control with predictors and pre-treatment outcomes synth cigsale /// lnincome age15to24 beer retprice /// cigsale(1975) cigsale(1980) cigsale(1988), /// trunit(3) trperiod(1988) /// mspeperiod(1970(1)1988) resultsperiod(1970(1)2000) /// keep(synth_ca.dta) replace fig
* Display weight matrix mat list e(V_matrix)
* Save the synthetic control graph graph save Graph synth_ca.gph, replace

&lt;/div&gt;

    &lt;!-- 卡片2: Gap Analysis --&gt;
    &lt;div class="method-card"&gt;
