        &lt;div class="code-block"&gt;
* Plot the gap in predicted error use synth_ca.dta, clear keep _Y_treated _Y_synthetic _time drop if _time==. rename _time year rename _Y_treated treat rename _Y_synthetic counterfact gen gap3 = treat - counterfact
* Create gap plot with reference lines sort year twoway (line gap3 year, lp(solid) lw(thick) lcolor(black)), /// yline(0, lpattern(shortdash) lcolor(black)) /// xline(1988, lpattern(shortdash) lcolor(black)) /// xtitle(““, si(medsmall)) /// xlabel(#10) /// ytitle(”Gap in per-capita cigarette sales (in packs)“, size(medsmall)) /// legend(off)
save synth_3.dta, replace
